<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-2623] CLI escaped single quote parsing gives errors</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-2623</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Escaping quotes in cli commands causes parsing errors.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;some examples::::&lt;br/&gt;
No need to create columns etc, it doesn&apos;t get through parsing the expression::&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;cassandra-cli&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1. &lt;br/&gt;
set column&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;#39;KEY+vals&amp;#39;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;VALUE&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; = &apos;VAL\&apos;&apos; ;&lt;br/&gt;
Syntax error at position 41: mismatched character &apos;&amp;lt;EOF&amp;gt;&apos; expecting &apos;&apos;&apos;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2.&lt;br/&gt;
set column&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;#39;KEY+val\&amp;#39;s&amp;#39;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;VALUE&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; = &apos;VAL&apos; ;&lt;br/&gt;
Syntax error at position 41: mismatched character &apos;&amp;lt;EOF&amp;gt;&apos; expecting &apos;&apos;&apos;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;3.&lt;br/&gt;
set column&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;#39;KEY+vals\&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;VALUE&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; = &apos;VAL\&apos;&apos; ;&lt;br/&gt;
Syntax error at position 38: unexpected &quot;\&quot; for `set column&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;#39;KEY+vals\&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;VALUE&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; = &apos;VAL\&apos;&apos; ;`.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;windows vista, linux&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
